data.description: Amazing location for anyone needing quick access to Hartsfield International Airport. This townhome is move in ready and outfitted with new carpet cleaning, fresh paint throughout the entire townhome and newly inserted toilet seats! The townhome has been professionally cleaned as well. Well cared for community with grounds maintained by HOA, this is low maintenance at its best and a great value! Plenty of storage here!  Master upstairs is a true retreat with walk in closet and en suite!  Make your move today!
